title: Tiger Zinda Hai
subTitle: RAW Agent Tiger joins forces with Zoya in order to rescue a group of nurses who are held hostage by a terrorist organisation.

title: Rocky
subTitle: After his father's death, a traumatised Rakesh is adopted by a Christian couple who rename him, Rocky. Years later, he realises his true identity and vows to avenge his father's murder.

title: Hanuman vs. Mahiravana
subTitle: Lord Hanuman goes to save Goddess Sita and defeat the king of Lanka, Ravana. To defend his kingdom, Ravana unleashes his most powerful ally, his brother, Mahiravana.

title: Trishul
subTitle: Born out of wedlock, Vijay grows up with deep resentment towards his biological father Raj, a wealthy industrialist who has been leading a comfortable life with his legitimate family in the big city.

title: Chandni
subTitle: Rohit sets out to find his former lover, whom he leaves due to his accident. When he meets her, he finds out she is engaged to marry her boss.

title: Stree
subTitle: In the eerie townscape of Chanderi, dressmaker Vicky falls for a mysterious woman with a supernatural aura. His heart sinks at the possibility that she might be Stree, the resentful man-hunter.

title: Souten
subTitle: Shyam, a middle-class man, falls in love with a millionaire's daughter and marries her. However, as their relationship starts deteriorating, Shyam finds solace in the company of Radha.

title: Swarg
subTitle: Krishna worships his master, Sahabji, but circumstances lead to his ouster from the house. He works hard, becomes a powerful man and returns to restore his master's honour.

title: Baaghi 2
subTitle: Ronny, a soldier, learns of the disappearance of the daughter of his former lover. Soon, his intense investigation leads him to uncover a web of crimes and a secret from the past.

title: Baaghi 2
subTitle: Ronny, a soldier, learns of the disappearance of the daughter of his former lover. Soon, his intense investigation leads him to uncover a web of crimes and a secret from the past.

title: The Burning Train
subTitle: Vinod, a railway engineer, launches the Super Express, a dream project that is India's fastest passenger train. However, it goes out of control on its maiden journey due to a bomb planted by a rival.

title: Bal Hanuman 4: Attack of the Universe
subTitle: When Chote Maharaj arranges an intense kabaddi tournament between monkeys and crocodiles, the treacherous reptiles conspire to resurrect their demon king using support from extraterrestrial allies.

title: Sanam Bewafa
subTitle: Salman and Rukhsar's love brings two warring families face to face, only for tradition, dowry demands and heartbreak to test their fragile bond.

title: Dushmani
subTitle: Suraj and Sapna, lovers belonging to enemy families, find their relationship threatened by bullets and betrayal when their brothers collide.

title: Sapne Saajan Ke
subTitle: Shalini, who has always wanted her daughter, Jyoti, to marry a rich man, is happy that she has found Deepak to be her life partner. However, no one knows that he is only pretending to be wealthy.

title: Mann
subTitle: Dev and Priya fall in love despite being engaged to their respective partners and decide to reunite after six months to get married. However, destiny has other plans for them.

title: Rakshak
subTitle: ASP Raj Sinha is assigned to catch the criminal responsible for printing and circulating fake currency notes. However, he is shocked to learn that the person is none other than his childhood friend.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.

title: Salma Pe Dil Aagaya
subTitle: Two youngsters from warring tribes fall in love with each other. They believe their problems are over when a mediator helps their families to patch up, unaware of a man who had taken advantage of the enmity.

title: Jurmana
subTitle: A flambouyant businessman places a bet with his former college friend to woo their professor's young daughter. However, the bet leads to a series of unexpected consequences.

title: Suhaag
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Jamai Raja
subTitle: When the wealthy Durgeshwari's daughter falls in love with Raja, a poor boy, she reluctantly agrees to their union. However, she constantly tries to sabotage their relationship, but Raja outwits her.

title: Vardi
subTitle: Constable Bhagwan is killed by Lalchand, a gangster. Years later, Bhagwan's son Ajay, along with his father's close associate Inspector Verma, tries to capture Lalchand and bring him to justice.

title: Rishtey
subTitle: A man marries his lover and has a child with her against the wishes of her wealthy father. However, his scheming father-in-law ruins their marriage and leaves to care for his boy by himself.

title: Yodha
subTitle: Karan, a lawyer, and Suraj, a victim of fate, find themselves fighting for the same cause when they take on the anti-social elements to rid the society of its ills.

title: Dhol
subTitle: Four lazy friends want to make easy money and aim to marry a rich girl. Their plan backfires after they meet Ritu and get embroiled with a dangerous criminal.
